textBox.richText: Andrew Kolody shared this with me and I finally understand the beef going on between Ultra Music Festival and the Winter Music Conference. I am going to be in Miami for the WMC this coming year, working as a brand ambassador for our sponsor. After reading this article, I am glad to be supporting WMC on this one. http://www.houseplanet.dj/index.php/November-2010/Louis-Puig-Club-Space-Miami-owner-writes-about-WMC-2011-drama.html
